Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.27,0:23:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要不要在这里干一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.85,0:23:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多关照了 朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.72,0:23:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也？
